I quit fighting! You guys want to put the screws on, go ahead.

156
00:14:13,652 --> 00:14:17,645
 你想做什么，我能忍受  好了，普威特
  I can take anything you dish out.   Okay, Prewitt.

157
00:14:25,130 --> 00:14:26,620
