  Don't forget it.   I won't forget it.

167
00:15:13,279 --> 00:15:17,181
华登是怎么回事？ 我不了解他
What's the deal with Warden? I don't figure him.

168
00:15:21,353 --> 00:15:24,151
他不像别人
He ain't like the others.

169
00:15:25,524 --> 00:15:27,458
他会对你很严厉
He'll make it tough on you.

170
00:15:27,660 --> 00:15:31,687
但他会划定一条公平界线 而且会谨守份际
But he'll draw a line he thinks fair and won't cross it.

171
00:15:32,464 --> 00:15:35,490
现在很少有这种军士长了
You don't see many topkicks like him no more.

172
00:15:36,201 --> 00:15:39,693
他在十五军团时 在上海作战
He was with the 15th in Shanghai when they saw action.

173
00:15:39,905 --> 00:15:42,203
连在菲律宾的我 也听说过他的战绩
I heard about it in the Philippines.

174
00:15:42,408 --> 00:15:46,105
我只知道 他是我见过最好的军人
All I know is he's the best soldier I ever saw.

175
00:16:10,135 --> 00:16:14,094
 答数！继续答数  1，2，3，4
  Count, keep count!   One, two, three, four.

176
00:16:16,175 --> 00:16:17,904
