Prewitt! One step forward, march!

179
00:16:44,803 --> 00:16:49,297
你的步法好像喝醉的鸟一样 我来教你出操！留在原地
You march like a drunken bird! I'll teach you to drill. Stay here.

180
00:16:49,508 --> 00:16:52,671
