如果你想找上尉，他不在家
If you're looking for the captain, he isn't here.

204
00:20:45,844 --> 00:20:50,076
 假设我找的不是他呢？  他还是不在
  And if I'm not looking for him?   He's still not here.

205
00:20:50,282 --> 00:20:53,445
