I am looking for him. Do you know where he is?

206
00:20:53,652 --> 00:20:57,782
我不晓得 或许他又“到城里公干”
I haven't any idea. Perhaps he's "in town on business."

207
00:20:57,990 --> 00:21:00,982
前几天你是这么说的，对吧？
That's how you put it the other day, isn't it?

208
00:21:01,193 --> 00:21:04,685
