  Are these really important?   Yes. But tomorrow's okay.

218
00:22:14,933 --> 00:22:18,369
我还有副本，很容易就能处理
I got copies. It'll be easy to fix them.

219
00:22:19,471 --> 00:22:22,599
我喜欢，上士 你很有自信
I like that, sergeant. You have confidence.

220
00:22:22,808 --> 00:22:27,939
