或许你只误判了一件事 那就是夫人我
You probably only got one thing wrong. The lady herself.

232
00:23:11,323 --> 00:23:13,757
或许我并不像外表那样
The lady's not what she seems.

233
00:23:13,959 --> 00:23:17,827
