Not if I can help it.

237
00:23:34,012 --> 00:23:35,536
你在做什么？
What are you doing?

238
00:23:38,483 --> 00:23:41,611
我要走了 那不是你所希望的吗？
I'm leaving. Isn't that what you want?

239
00:23:42,988 --> 00:23:47,084
我不知道，上士 我不知道
I don't know, sergeant. I don't know.

240
00:24:24,095 --> 00:24:27,622
 快一点  我是很快！发薪日…
  Speed it up.   I am. Payday, payday.

241
00:24:29,568 --> 00:24:33,231
