Come on, buddy boy, we're going to town.

244
00:25:04,002 --> 00:25:06,470
别让他们惹恼你
Don't let them get your goat.

245
00:25:06,671 --> 00:25:10,801
我们可以穿便服 看起来跟别人一样帅
We'll dress in civvies and we're as good as everybody else.

246
00:25:13,345 --> 00:25:15,176
来！穿这件
Here, wear this.

247
00:25:16,715 --> 00:25:20,845
是我姐姐寄来的 她买的东西都太大了些
My sister sent it to me. She buys everything too big.

248
00:25:24,356 --> 00:25:26,517
我们先去几家酒吧逛逛
First we hit a few bars.

249
00:25:26,725 --> 00:25:29,558
我是新国会俱乐部的会员
I'm a member of The New Congress Club.

250
00:25:29,928 --> 00:25:34,388
女孩们！你对女人有偏见吗？
Girls! You got any prejudices against girls?

251
