That's par for the course here.

267
00:26:44,502 --> 00:26:48,768
我不在意 我从不曾有过秘密恋情
I don't care for it. I never went in for back alley loving.

268
00:26:48,974 --> 00:26:50,999
放轻松
Take it easy.

