So do I.

454
00:44:41,545 --> 00:44:45,606
 真好笑，不是吗？  是的，是很好笑
  That's funny, ain't it?   Yeah, that is funny.

455
00:44:51,121 --> 00:44:54,818
保持一直线，普威特
Keep going in a straight line, Prewitt.

456
00:44:56,060 --> 00:44:57,652
继续走！
Keep going!

457
00:45:04,268 --> 00:45:06,896
好了！够了
All right, that's enough.

458
00:45:18,749 --> 00:45:22,515
普威特！把它埋了
Okay, Prewitt, bury it.

459
00:46:20,944 --> 00:46:22,434
时间到
Time!

460
00:46:38,962 --> 00:46:42,261
把这里清干净，普威特
Clean up the mess, Prewitt.

461
00:46:42,466 --> 00:46:46,027
快！这是劳动！可不是在度假
Hurry up! You're on fatigue detail, not a vacation.

462
00:46:56,880 --> 00:46:58,370
快点！把它清干净
Come on! Clean it up!

463
00:46:59,116 --> 00:47:01,380
你自己清
Clean it up yourself!

464
00:47:01,552 --> 00:47:04,885
 什么？  要清你自己去清理
  What?   Rub your own nose in it a while.

465
00:47:05,088 --> 00:47:08,649
你不该跟无委任状士官顶嘴
You shouldn't talk back to a noncommissioned officer.

466
00:47:08,826 --> 00:47:13,456
但我可不喜欢 被无委任士官侮辱
But I don't like being spit on by a noncommissioned officer.

467
00:47:13,664 --> 00:47:15,928
 你应该向他道歉  绝不，长官
  You owe him an apology.   No, sir.

468
00:47:16,133 --> 00:47:18,260
是他该向我道歉
He owes me an apology.

469
00:47:18,435 --> 00:47:20,027
 帕路索下士  是的，长官
  Corporal Peluso?   Yes, sir.

470
00:47:20,237 --> 00:47:25,869
让这个人全副武装 带他去跑可洛可洛山路
Have this man roll a full field pack and hike him up to Kolekole Pass.

471
00:47:26,076 --> 00:47:28,544
 然后再带他来见我  是的，长官
  And then bring him to me.   Yes, sir.

472
00:47:28,745 --> 00:47:31,475
 好了，普威特！我们走  时间
  All right, Prewitt, let's go.   Time!

473
00:47:41,725 --> 00:47:43,420
等一下
Hold it a minute.

474
00:47:47,331 --> 00:47:52,769
抽根烟吧 我跟你一样不喜欢这种事
Go ahead, have a cigarette. I don't like this any more than you.

475
00:47:55,973 --> 00:47:59,500
你预备好向 葛罗维奇士官道歉？
You're ready to apologize to Sergeant Galovitch now?

476
00:47:59,710 --> 00:48:01,507
不，长官！我不道歉
No, sir, I'm not.

477
00:48:02,980 --> 00:48:07,440
 帕路索！再带他去跑一圈  是的，长官
  Peluso, take him up there again.   Yes, sir.

478
00:48:07,651 --> 00:48:10,381
好了，普威特！我们走
All right, Prewitt, let's go.

479
00:48:25,369 --> 00:48:29,738
你不能善待这种人 他好像是头野兽似的
You can't be decent to a man like that! He's like an animal.

480
00:48:33,143 --> 00:48:37,603
上士，准备军法审判的表格 罪名是抗命
Sergeant, prepare court martial papers. Insubordination.

481
00:48:37,814 --> 00:48:39,441
是的，长官
Yes, sir.

482
00:48:50,460 --> 00:48:52,951
 只是太可惜了  怎么了？
  Only it's a shame.   What is?

483
00:48:53,163 --> 00:48:55,791
你将会失去一名中量级好手
You'll lose a good middleweight.

484
00:48:55,966 --> 00:48:58,093
我不需要忍受他的无礼
I don't have to stand for insolence!

485
00:48:58,302 --> 00:49:01,237
不，长官！当然用不着
No, sir, you sure don't.

486
00:49:02,973 --> 00:49:05,840
我马上准备表格
I'll prepare the papers then.

487
00:49:06,176 --> 00:49:12,115
就算他只被判刑三个月 决赛时他会待在禁闭室中
Even if he gets three months, he'll still be in stockade for the finals.

488
00:49:12,282 --> 00:49:15,251
你有办法说服他吗？
Do you see any other way of breaking him?

489
00:49:17,187 --> 00:49:19,246
你可以加重惩罚，长官
You could double punishment, sir.

490
00:49:19,456 --> 00:49:24,689
 我会用重刑  如果你那么觉得的话，长官
  I'll throw the book at him.   Lf you think that's the way, sir.

491
00:49:33,570 --> 00:49:36,130
好建议！上士
Nice going, sarge.

492
00:49:36,340 --> 00:49:40,174
继续看的话 你会发现自己在刷地板
Keep looking, you'll find yourself scrubbing this floor!

493
00:49:57,494 --> 00:49:58,688
借过！
Coming through!

494
00:49:58,895 --> 00:50:03,355
我和服务生们已经忙坏了 烫！烫！
Me and my waiters are working our tails off. Hot! Hot!

495
00:50:06,837 --> 00:50:10,671
你好吗？在这里比被关禁闭好
How you doing? It's better than being in the stockade.

496
00:50:13,143 --> 00:50:15,407
我好吗？我是个粗人
How am I doing? I'm a rough man.

497
00:50:15,612 --> 00:50:17,910
慢一点！汗别滴到菜上
Slow down. Don't sweat in the food.

498
00:50:18,115 --> 00:50:21,175
不要阻止我 我正在申请升下士
Don't hold me back. I'm putting in for corporal.

499
00:50:21,385 --> 00:50:23,114
你成功不了的
You'll never make it.

500
00:50:36,900 --> 00:50:39,095
一生都得待在步兵团里
Life in a rifle company.

501
00:50:41,471 --> 00:50:43,439
你看起来很累的样子，小子
You look awful tired, kid.

502
00:50:45,308 --> 00:50:47,242
你喜欢连续当班吗？
How do you like straight duty?

503
00:50:47,444 --> 00:50:50,675
 你认为我会介意吗？  我没有那么说
  You think I mind it?   I didn't say that.

504
00:50:50,881 --> 00:50:54,476
我只是说你看来很累的样子 好像快崩溃似的
I just said you looked tired. Drawn to a fine edge.

505
00:50:54,918 --> 00:50:57,182
我喜欢这种生活！棒极了
I like this life. It's great.

506
00:50:57,387 --> 00:51:01,346
如果我找到珍珠，我会算你一份 跟你平分，知道吗？
If I find a pearl, I'll cut you in. 50 50, you know?

507
00:51:01,558 --> 00:51:04,891
如果不是你让我来这里 我不会有机会去找它
If you didn't put me here, I'd have no chance to find it.

508
00:51:05,095 --> 00:51:07,427
你真是的
There's a man for you.

509
00:51:07,631 --> 00:51:10,623
既然你喜欢 我会再多替你找一些
Since you like it, I'll find more for you.

510
00:51:10,834 --> 00:51:14,565
 垃圾小队怎么样？  谢了！礼拜三已经做过了
  How about garbage detail?   Thanks, I had that on Wednesday.

511
00:51:14,771 --> 00:51:17,934
原来做过了 那么扫街如何？
So you did. What about street cleaning?

512
00:51:18,642 --> 00:51:21,873
 昨天扫过了  你的记忆力比我的更好
  Yesterday.   You got a better memory than me.

513
00:51:22,045 --> 00:51:26,038
 当然！如果你聪明的话…  说得是！但我并不聪明
  Of course, if you were smart...   Yeah, but I ain't smart.

514
00:51:26,249 --> 00:51:29,309
但如果你聪明 你就用不着做炊事兵
But if you were, you wouldn't have to pull K.P.

515
00:51:29,519 --> 00:51:32,215
或者其他劳动工作
Or any other fatigue duty for that matter.

516
00:51:32,422 --> 00:51:36,256
如果你认为可以说服我打拳 那你就错了
If you think you can bribe me into boxing, you're wrong.

517
00:51:36,460 --> 00:51:41,193
你错了！你没有办法 荷姆斯跟特训也办不到
You're wrong. Not you and Dynamite Holmes and the Treatment.

518
00:51:48,038 --> 00:51:51,439
你还要压迫普威特多久？
How long will you keep breaking it off on Prewitt?

519
00:51:51,608 --> 00:51:56,739
你已连续一个月罚他加班了 我不明白为什么你…
You've had him on extra duty for a month. I can't see why you...

520
00:51:56,913 --> 00:52:00,212
年纪大心也变软了吗？ 或许我是在给他些教训
Getting soft in your old age? Maybe I'm teaching him a lesson.

521
00:52:00,417 --> 00:52:02,510
 或许是你喜欢这样  或许我是喜欢
  Maybe you like it.   Maybe I do.

522
00:52:02,853 --> 00:52:06,949
我不想再看你做荷姆斯的爪牙
I'm getting tired of watching you being a stooge for Holmes.

523
00:52:07,157 --> 00:52:09,182
你不会再看多久了
You won't see it much longer.

524
00:52:09,392 --> 00:52:13,920
我自己也很厌烦 我随时都可以不干！真的
I'm tired of it myself. I'm through, any day now. I mean it!

525
00:52:14,131 --> 00:52:17,100
只要荷姆斯允许 我宁可明天就请调
If Holmes'd let me, I'd transfer out tomorrow.

526
00:52:17,300 --> 00:52:20,428
有半打以上的军团会争取我 而且还会有官阶
Half a dozen companies would grab me. In grade too.

527
00:52:20,637 --> 00:52:23,162
当然！我还可以做参谋长
Sure. I could be chief of staff too.

528
00:52:23,373 --> 00:52:27,673
 但我不能离开我的弟兄  你要上哪儿去？应声虫
  Only I just can't leave my buddies.   Where you going, Little Sir Echo?

529
00:52:27,878 --> 00:52:31,245
去冲澡！除非士官长反对
To shower, unless the stinking first sergeant objects.

530
00:52:31,448 --> 00:52:34,940
 你以为了呢？去看电影吗？  快点！我们去喝几杯啤酒
  What'd you think? To the movies?   Hurry up. We'll get some beer.

531
00:52:35,152 --> 00:52:37,677
就算那是世上最后的啤酒也不去
Not if it was the last beer in the world.

532
00:52:37,888 --> 00:52:39,480
我请客
I'm buying.

533
00:52:40,323 --> 00:52:41,813
那就不一样了
That's different.

534
00:53:03,413 --> 00:53:04,744
萝丝
Rose.

535
00:53:07,150 --> 00:53:11,985
知道为何我喜欢你为我服务？ 这样我才能看着你走开
Know why I like to have you serve me? So I can watch you walk away.

536
00:53:15,358 --> 00:53:20,853
你有权抱怨 你可以去向督察长申诉
You got a right to complain, to take it to the inspector general.

537
00:53:21,064 --> 00:53:23,897
任何士兵都可以 就连普通二等兵都行
Any soldier has, even a plain dogface.

538
00:53:24,100 --> 00:53:27,433
不！我不会去申诉
Nope. I ain't going to complain.

539
00:53:27,704 --> 00:53:30,468
我不会让他们得到满足的
They ain't going to get that satisfaction.

540
00:53:33,944 --> 00:53:38,847
我有一大家人，一共十五人 这里只有一半而已
I've got a real big family, 15 of them. This is only half.

541
00:53:39,049 --> 00:53:42,041
你看到那个留八字胡的先生？
You see the gentleman with the handlebars?

542
00:53:42,252 --> 00:53:44,413
那是我父亲，马吉欧先生
That's Mr. Maggio, my father.

543
00:53:47,891 --> 00:53:51,952
从没见过如此顽固的人 离他们上次让你进城有多久了？
Never saw anybody so stubborn. How long since they let you go to town?

544
00:53:52,162 --> 00:53:54,392
 六个星期  搞不好会六年
  Six weeks.   It's liable to be six years.

545
00:53:54,598 --> 00:53:59,592
 六年你都看不到女人  你何不管好自己的事？
  Six years before you see a dame.   Why don't you mind your own business?

546
00:53:59,803 --> 00:54:02,499
你为什么不去学吹号角？
And why don't you learn to play the bugle?

547
00:54:38,174 --> 00:54:39,732
那才是我的好兄弟
That's my buddy boy!

548
00:54:54,791 --> 00:54:58,420
 这小妞是谁？  是我姐姐
  Who's the broad?   It's my sister.

549
00:55:12,809 --> 00:55:16,245
 你打我  没错！而且我会再打
  You hit me!   Yeah, and I'm about to do it again.

550
00:55:18,548 --> 00:55:20,277
你这个肮脏的意大利佬
Why, you dirty wop!

551
00:55:20,483 --> 00:55:23,816
 到外面解决  我要切下这义佬的心脏
  Take it outside!   I'll cut this wop's heart out.

552
00:55:24,020 --> 00:55:27,148
如果有人敢插手 我会先修理他
Anybody steps in here, I'll give it to him first.

553
00:55:28,692 --> 00:55:31,820
再往前一步，胖子 我就会砍了你的脑袋
One step further, Fatso, and I'll de brain you.

554
00:55:32,062 --> 00:55:34,860
这里只有我才可以杀人
Anybody does any killing here, I'll do it!

555
00:55:35,065 --> 00:55:39,468
 这是私事  不！他属于我的军团
  This is a private affair.   No, it ain't! He's in my company.

556
00:55:39,669 --> 00:55:43,230
不要无缘无故的替我制造麻烦
You ain't making two extra weeks of paperwork for me.

557
00:55:44,207 --> 00:55:47,335
非打不可吗？ 搞不好会把胆汁都吐出来
Out for blood? You'd puke your guts out.

558
00:55:47,544 --> 00:55:49,068
把凳子放下
Put down that stool.

559
00:55:49,279 --> 00:55:50,712
把它放下
Put it down!

560
00:55:56,319 --> 00:55:57,809
把刀子扔掉
Drop that knife.

561
00:56:02,125 --> 00:56:06,459
好吧！胖子！ 如果你想杀人就来吧！
Okay, Fatso, if it's killing you want, come on.

562
00:56:08,031 --> 00:56:09,555
来吧！
Well, come on.

563
00:56:14,971 --> 00:56:16,461
丢到地板上
On the floor!

564
00:56:28,818 --> 00:56:33,346
杀手？我宁可用你们 来交换一个女童军
Killers, huh? I'd trade the pair of you for a good Campfire Girl!

565
00:56:41,965 --> 00:56:43,592
泼猴
Tough monkey.

566
00:56:44,434 --> 00:56:47,892
你这种人迟早会被关禁闭
Guys like you end up in the stockade sooner or later.

567
00:56:48,071 --> 00:56:51,040
总有一天我会等着你被关进来
Someday you'll walk in, I'll be waiting.

568
00:56:51,241 --> 00:56:53,869
到时我会要你好看
I'll show you a couple of things.

569
00:57:12,662 --> 00:57:14,892
我要出去呼吸点空气
I'm going to get a breath of air.

570
00:57:24,174 --> 00:57:25,903
我很高兴他阻止了这件事
I'm glad he stopped it.

571
00:57:27,110 --> 00:57:28,702
他是个好人
A good man.

572
00:57:48,631 --> 00:57:52,032
你留着！留做纪念
You keep it. Keep it for a souvenir.

573
00:57:53,670 --> 00:57:55,797
好吧！我会留着
Okay, I'll keep it.

574
00:57:56,005 --> 00:57:58,997
你不太有机会享受生活吧？小子
You ain't enjoying life much, are you, kid?

575
00:58:07,650 --> 00:58:11,677
 你周末想放假吗？  可以吗？
  Could you stand a weekend pass?   Could I?

576
00:58:13,857 --> 00:58:15,290
荷姆斯怎么办？
What about Holmes?

577
00:58:15,492 --> 00:58:19,292
别担心！我放在他面前的文件 他都会签字
Don't worry. He signs anything I put in front of him.

578
00:58:19,496 --> 00:58:21,361
我会用的到的
I sure could use it.

579
00:58:26,536 --> 00:58:30,199
听说你迷恋上 新国会俱乐部一位小姐
I hear you're dippy over a dame at the New Congress Club.

580
00:58:30,406 --> 00:58:33,307
 她叫什么名字？  萝琳
  What'd you say her name was?   Lorene.

581
00:58:33,510 --> 00:58:35,171
好美的名字
Beautiful name.

582
00:58:51,794 --> 00:58:53,455
嗨！老兄
Hey, <i>paisan!</i>

583
00:58:53,730 --> 00:58:55,721
是什么绊住你了？我们走
What's holding you up? Let's go.

584
00:58:55,932 --> 00:58:59,129
怎么了？你不喜欢这里吗？
What's the matter? Don't you like it here?

585
00:58:59,435 --> 00:59:01,869
巴士就快开了！我要赶去搭车
The bus is leaving now. I'm taking it.

586
00:59:02,071 --> 00:59:05,097
快走！我是有钱人 我会搭计程车
Take off. I'm a rich man. I'll hop a taxi.

587
00:59:05,308 --> 00:59:07,970
我到卡拉库瓦跟你碰面
I'll meet you at the Kalakaua later.

588
00:59:17,687 --> 00:59:19,552
马吉欧！预备上哨
Maggio, get ready for guard!

589
00:59:19,856 --> 00:59:23,690
戴宽边毯帐，子弹腰带 武器！十分钟内报到
Campaign hat, cartridge belt, weapon! Report in 10 minutes.

590
00:59:23,893 --> 00:59:25,622
什么？我有假单
What?! I got a pass!

591
00:59:25,895 --> 00:59:28,227
那不算！安德生病了 所以你得上哨
Not anymore. Anderson's sick. You're on guard.

592
00:59:28,531 --> 00:59:30,499
我昨天上过哨，为什么是我？
I just had guard yesterday. Why me?

593
00:59:30,700 --> 00:59:34,568
我告诉你原因 你换衣服速度应该快一点
I'll tell you why. You should've gotten dressed faster.

594
00:59:41,778 --> 00:59:46,511
你在回避我吗？ 他们甚至不让我进来
You giving me the runaround? They didn't even want to let me in.

595
00:59:46,716 --> 00:59:52,382
这里有一大群希坎军营来的人 你到底想怎么样？
A big crowd from Hickam Field is here. Anyway, what'd you expect?

596
00:59:52,589 --> 00:59:55,990
 我以为你会想见我  我正在忙，看到了吗？
  I thought you'd want to see me.   I'm busy, see?

597
00:59:56,192 --> 00:59:58,490
 是的，我看到了  我是在忙
  Yes, I can see.   Well, I am.

598
01:00:00,797 --> 01:00:03,698
马吉欧待会儿会去卡拉库瓦
Look, Maggio will be at the Kalakaua later.

599
01:00:03,900 --> 01:00:06,698
难道你不能想办法离开吗？
Ain't there no way you can get out of here?

600
01:00:06,903 --> 01:00:11,340
你到底怎么搞的？ 我在这里工作，你不懂吗？
What's the matter with you? I work here. Can't you understand?

601
01:00:13,676 --> 01:00:15,200
是的，我当然明白
Yes, I do understand.

602
01:00:16,079 --> 01:00:18,138
我非常明白
I understand very well.

603
01:00:19,449 --> 01:00:22,111
你几个礼拜都没有来 现在突然出现…
You haven't been around here in weeks, and now you turn up all of a sudden...

604
01:00:22,318 --> 01:00:24,809
小心！老兄！走路要看路
Watch it, mac! Watch where you're going!

605
01:00:25,021 --> 01:00:26,784
我们到外面去
Come on out of here.

606
01:00:36,232 --> 01:00:39,167
奇佛太太有规定 我不能这样就走掉了
Mrs. Kipfer has rules. I can't just walk out.

607
01:00:39,369 --> 01:00:42,099
我们不能在外面跟男孩约会
We can't see the boys on the outside.

608
01:00:42,305 --> 01:00:45,035
如果你是这种感觉那就算了
If you feel that way, just forget about it.

609
01:00:45,241 --> 01:00:48,677
你管不着我 你又不是我丈夫
You haven't any claims on me. You're not my husband.

610
01:00:48,878 --> 01:00:53,144
原来你在这里，萝琳 我欣赏你的品味但我们需要她
There you are, Lorene. I admire your taste, dear, but we need her now.

611
01:00:53,349 --> 01:00:56,682
有许多位先生没有人陪伴 真是忙坏了
So many of the gentlemen are unattended. It is such a rush.

612
01:00:56,886 --> 01:01:00,378
搞不好有人会误解 我们在开大型政治会议
One might almost mistake us for a big political convention.

613
01:01:00,590 --> 01:01:03,582
 你来吧？萝琳  马上来
  You are coming, Lorene?   In a minute.

614
01:01:06,496 --> 01:01:08,054
对不起
I'm sorry.

615
01:01:08,264 --> 01:01:12,428
你认为我有什么感觉？ 搞不好我几个月都无法拿到假条
How do you think I feel? I may not get another pass for months.

616
01:01:12,635 --> 01:01:17,231
我期待这次见面 就像小孩期待耶诞节一样
I been counting on this like a kid counts on Christmas.

617
01:01:17,940 --> 01:01:21,467
还是算了吧！萝琳在忙 萝琳很抱歉
But forget it. Lorene's busy. Lorene's sorry.

618
01:01:21,678 --> 01:01:24,078
别再叫我萝琳 我的本名叫艾玛
Stop calling me Lorene! My name's Alma!

619
01:01:24,247 --> 01:01:25,839
 艾玛？  是的，艾玛伯克
  Alma?   Yes, Alma Burke!

620
01:01:26,049 --> 01:01:27,539
艾玛？
Alma?

621
01:01:30,420 --> 01:01:34,413
奇佛太太从香水广告上 挑了萝琳这个名字
Mrs. Kipfer picked "Lorene" out of a perfume ad.

622
01:01:35,158 --> 01:01:37,490
她觉得这个名字很有法国风味
She thought it sounded French.

623
01:01:56,979 --> 01:01:58,412
你怎么脱身的？
How did you get away?

624
01:01:58,614 --> 01:02:02,015
我说我病了 但我打赌她并不相信
I said I was sick. But I bet she doesn't believe it.

625
01:02:02,218 --> 01:02:04,880
 我赌她不信  你想喝什么？
  I bet she doesn't.   What'll you have?

626
01:02:05,088 --> 01:02:08,785
 可乐，谢谢  给她可乐，大可乐
  A Coke, please.   Give her a Coke, big Coke.

627
01:02:08,991 --> 01:02:11,482
你能来这里见我真好
It's great you meeting me here.

628
01:02:11,694 --> 01:02:15,186
我是运气好才能进城 军士长饶了我
I'm lucky to get to town. Topkick gave me a break.

629
01:02:15,398 --> 01:02:16,956
他们还在施压吗？
They still pouring it on?

630
01:02:17,166 --> 01:02:21,728
 他们真的让我快要崩溃  你一定很恨军队
  They really got me on the edge.   Gee, you must hate the Army.

631
01:02:21,938 --> 01:02:25,567
 不，我不恨它  但把你折磨成这样
  No, I don't hate it.   But look what it's doing to you.

632
01:02:26,509 --> 01:02:27,703
我爱军队
I love the Army.

633
01:02:29,178 --> 01:02:31,146
但它一定不爱你
But it sure doesn't love you.

634
01:02:32,482 --> 01:02:36,646
男人爱一样东西 并不表示一定有所回报
A man loves a thing, that don't mean it's got to love him back.

635
01:02:36,853 --> 01:02:39,913
没错，但人的忍耐有限
Yeah, but a person can stand just so much.

636
01:02:41,224 --> 01:02:43,590
你爱某件事，你应该感恩
You love a thing, you gotta be grateful.

637
01:02:43,793 --> 01:02:47,991
我在十七岁时离家 我的父母亲都死了
See, I left home when I was 17. Both my folks is dead.

638
01:02:48,197 --> 01:02:51,860
我没有归属感直到入伍为止
And I didn't belong no place till I entered the Army.

639
01:02:52,068 --> 01:02:54,628
而且我还学会吹号角
And I wouldn't have learned how to bugle.

640
01:02:54,837 --> 01:02:55,826
吹号角？
To bugle?

641
01:02:56,038 --> 01:03:01,135
这个吹口就是我在 阿灵顿公墓吹丧葬号时用的
That's the mouthpiece I used when I played a taps at Arlington.

642
01:03:02,512 --> 01:03:06,505
他们选我在休战纪念日 吹奏丧葬号角
They picked me to play a taps there on Armistice Day.

643
01:03:06,716 --> 01:03:08,616
总统也到场
The president was there.

644
01:03:11,621 --> 01:03:13,919
我的号角吹得很好
I play the bugle well.

645
01:03:14,123 --> 01:03:15,556
嗨！老百姓
Hello, citizens!

646
01:03:17,260 --> 01:03:18,784
你上哪儿去了？
Hey, where you been?

647
01:03:18,995 --> 01:03:22,726
我已经去过三家酒吧 我对三家酒吧都做了些奉献
I've been in three bars and I put a dent in all three.

648
01:03:22,932 --> 01:03:24,399
没错！看来就像
Yeah, you look it.

649
01:03:24,600 --> 01:03:28,058
 给我些酒  你怎么会穿制服？
  Give me a nail.   What you doing in uniform?

650
01:03:28,271 --> 01:03:30,762
我正考虑从军
I'm thinking of joining the Army.

651
01:03:31,507 --> 01:03:35,671
或许我该到墨西哥当牛仔 你愿意跟我一起去吗？
Or maybe I'll go to Mexico and become a cowboy. You want to go with me?

652
01:03:35,878 --> 01:03:40,042
你再继续喝酒 就会像溶掉的蜡烛一样游泳
You keep drinking, you'll be as much use as a melted candle.

653
01:03:41,017 --> 01:03:45,249
你说得很对 酒保！威士忌！大杯的
You're absolutely right. Bartender, whiskey! Large whiskey.

654
01:03:46,389 --> 01:03:49,085
借过，老兄
Excuse me. Hey, buddy.

655
01:03:49,992 --> 01:03:51,220
山姆
Sam!

656
01:03:52,461 --> 01:03:56,488
各位！金贝地下室的怪物 就要出笼了
Coming out, fellas, the terror of Gimbel's basement.

657
01:03:56,699 --> 01:04:00,157
让开！出个七点 五点，两点
Stand back now. A seven for Daddy. Five, deuce.

658
01:04:00,369 --> 01:04:02,200
七点
A seven.

659
01:04:03,206 --> 01:04:06,835
两个么点 那正是我一生的高潮
Snake eyes. That's the story of my life.

660
01:04:11,113 --> 01:04:14,310
夏威夷皇家饭店就在附近
That's the Royal Hawaiian around the corner.

661
01:04:14,517 --> 01:04:16,849
电影明星常在那里出现
Where all those movie stars stay.

662
01:04:17,019 --> 01:04:20,921
你最好安静下来 你还有整个周末要过
You better simmer down. You got a whole weekend ahead of you.

663
01:04:21,123 --> 01:04:22,988
那是你说的，兄弟
That's what you say, buddy.

664
01:04:23,192 --> 01:04:26,821
 他们只给你过夜假条吗？  没有假条
  They only gave you an overnight pass?   No pass.

665
01:04:27,163 --> 01:04:31,293
他们让我上哨 可是老安杰罗骗过他们了
They put me on guard duty. But old Angelo, he foxed them.

666
01:04:31,868 --> 01:04:33,335
你擅离岗哨？
You walked off guard?

667
01:04:33,536 --> 01:04:35,766
我签到之后立刻签出
I checked in and checked right out.

668
01:04:35,972 --> 01:04:39,499
你赶快回到岗哨去 你的麻烦大了
You get your tail back to the post. You're in trouble.

669
01:04:39,709 --> 01:04:43,941
我有个好主意 我们去跟电影明星游泳
I got a good idea. Let's go swimming with a movie star.

670
01:04:44,146 --> 01:04:47,513
我正打算那么做 去跟电影明星游泳
That's what I'll do, go swimming with a movie star!

671
01:04:47,717 --> 01:04:50,880
二十英尺高 我要去跟电影明星游泳
Twenty feet tall. I'm swimming with a movie star.

672
01:04:53,055 --> 01:04:54,716
你最好快走吧！
You better go.

673
01:05:09,639 --> 01:05:12,301
混球！快走来！醒醒
You jerk, get up. Wake up!

674
01:05:12,508 --> 01:05:14,601
我是清醒的！你干嘛大吼？
I'm awake. Why are you hollering?

675
01:05:14,810 --> 01:05:16,903
把衣服穿上
Put your clothes on.

676
01:05:17,113 --> 01:05:20,480
把它们送给印第安人 他们会需要的
Give them back to the Indians. They need them.

677
01:05:20,683 --> 01:05:22,844
他们只穿丁字裤
All they wear is G strings.

678
01:05:24,086 --> 01:05:26,281
你没有喝醉！快起来
You ain't drunk. Get up.

679
01:05:27,256 --> 01:05:32,717
我要在这里等电影明星 从饭店里出来
I am waiting here for a movie star to come out of the hotel...

680
01:05:32,929 --> 01:05:35,898
除非她出现否则我不会走
...and I'm not going until she shows up.

681
01:05:36,098 --> 01:05:37,895
把衣服穿上
Put your clothes on.

682
01:05:38,935 --> 01:05:42,029
在我们惹上麻烦之前赶快离开
Let's get out of here before we get in trouble.

683
01:05:42,238 --> 01:05:45,901
你是怎么回事？ 难道我不能喝醉吗？
What's the matter with you? Can't a man get drunk?

684
01:05:46,108 --> 01:05:48,008
难道我不能做自己想做的事？
Can't a man do nothing?

685
01:05:48,878 --> 01:05:54,316
难道我不能手插在口袋里 走在大街上吗？
Can't he put his lousy hands in his lousy pockets on a lousy street?

686
01:05:54,517 --> 01:05:57,213
难道我必须一生被追逐吗？
A man got to be hounded all his life?

687
01:05:57,420 --> 01:06:00,048
我累了！我又不是罪犯
Well, I'm tired. I ain't no criminal.

688
01:06:00,256 --> 01:06:02,918
 我也不是懦夫  兄弟，你瞧
  I ain't no coward!   Buddy boy, look.

689
01:06:04,860 --> 01:06:07,727
你把衣服穿好 快把衣服穿上
You get dressed. You put your clothes on.

690
01:06:08,297 --> 01:06:10,993
 等我！我去叫计程车  是才怪
  Wait for me, I'll get a cab.   Yeah, sure.

691
01:06:11,200 --> 01:06:13,862
 你会等吧？  是的，你去叫计程车
  Will you wait?   Yeah, you get a cab.

692
01:06:29,185 --> 01:06:30,777
嗨！宪兵
Hey, MPs!

693
01:06:30,987 --> 01:06:34,047
你们快来抓我！我在这里
Come and get me, you guys! Here I am!

694
01:06:39,261 --> 01:06:43,220
你们只能这样吗？ 我想你们一定是吃脆麦片的
Is that the best you can do? I bet you guys eat Wheaties!

695
01:06:52,575 --> 01:06:54,702
军事法庭有消息吗？
Any word on the court martial?

696
01:06:54,910 --> 01:06:56,571
现在正在审
It's on right now.

697
01:06:56,779 --> 01:06:59,179
他一定会被关禁闭
He'll get the stockade sure.

698
01:07:00,916 --> 01:07:04,943
或许他不会被关 他只不过是喝醉了
Maybe he won't get it. All he did was to get drunk.

699
01:07:05,154 --> 01:07:08,988
那是军人的本色 偶尔变成义务了
It's a soldier's nature, almost a duty once in a while.

700
01:07:09,191 --> 01:07:10,988
可是他擅离职守
But he went AWOL.

701
01:07:11,193 --> 01:07:13,821
 你为什么在这里？  男子汉不能休息吗？
  Why are you here?   Can't a man rest?

702
01:07:14,030 --> 01:07:18,194
什么男子汉？你没事做吗？ 我可以派一些给你
What man? You got no work? Maybe I can scare you up some.

703
01:07:25,074 --> 01:07:28,703
去打几杆撞球 有任何消息我会通知你
Go shoot some pool. Any word comes, I'll let you know.

704
01:07:32,448 --> 01:07:35,417
参谋本部，华登上士 是的，长官
Company G, First Sergeant Warden. Yes, sir.

705
01:07:40,990 --> 01:07:43,322
我会把他的东西准备好
I'll have his things in order.

706
01:07:46,629 --> 01:07:48,654
他被判刑了，六个月
He got it. Six months.

707
01:08:01,077 --> 01:08:05,036
金贝的地下室关不了我 禁闭室也一样关不住
Gimbel's basement couldn't hold me, neither can this stockade.

708
01:08:05,247 --> 01:08:07,772
 闭嘴！  全听你的，女童军
  Shut up!   Whatever you say, Brownie.

709
01:08:09,051 --> 01:08:11,110
囚犯！停
Prisoner, halt!

710
01:08:13,989 --> 01:08:15,854
警卫士官长

711
01:08:28,471 --> 01:08:30,234
你好，泼猴
Hello, tough monkey.

712
01:08:45,221 --> 01:08:49,954
我们很幸运能租到它 这是个迎合潮流的好区
We were lucky to rent it. This is a very fashionable district.

713
01:08:51,694 --> 01:08:53,457
我替你打了钥匙
I had a key made for you.

714
01:08:53,662 --> 01:08:57,257
你随时都可以用它 就算我不在也可以
You can use it any time, even when I'm not here.

715
01:09:08,477 --> 01:09:12,311
普威特就是我跟你提起的大兵 乔琪特，我的室友
Prew is the soldier I told you about. Georgette, my roommate.

716
01:09:12,515 --> 01:09:13,777
欢迎你，朋友
Welcome, friend.

717
01:09:13,983 --> 01:09:17,350
自从那只猫死了以后 屋里就没有男的了
There hasn't been a man around the house since the cat died.

718
01:09:17,553 --> 01:09:20,488
我每次必订阅书会的书
I always take every book from the Book Club.

719
01:09:20,689 --> 01:09:23,283
那是我分得红利的方式
That's the way I get all the dividends.

720
01:09:24,527 --> 01:09:27,826
等马吉欧出禁闭室后 她会很适合他
She'll be great for Maggio when he gets out.

721
01:09:28,030 --> 01:09:30,498
是的，他会为她疯狂
Yes, he'll be crazy about her.

722
01:09:33,169 --> 01:09:35,729
请坐！让自己舒服一下
Just sit down and get comfortable.

723
01:09:35,938 --> 01:09:39,101
我去替你调杯马丁尼 再去准备晚饭
I'll make you a martini and see about dinner.

724
01:09:39,308 --> 01:09:42,744
感觉好像结了婚，对吧？
This is like being married, ain't it?

725
01:09:42,945 --> 01:09:44,537
好比结了婚
It's better.

726
01:10:04,700 --> 01:10:06,190
你还好吗？
You okay?

727
01:10:28,123 --> 01:10:29,784
很高兴你来了吗？
Glad you came?

728
01:10:59,555 --> 01:11:02,353
我们走吧！不要回头
Let's get out of here. Don't look around.

729
01:11:38,027 --> 01:11:40,587
我们不能再这样继续下去
It can't go on like this much longer.

730
01:11:42,431 --> 01:11:45,730
就算是到了岛这一头 我们还是得…
Even clear across the island, we had to...

731
01:11:46,068 --> 01:11:48,502
像囚犯一样逃跑
...run out like jail birds.

732
01:11:53,676 --> 01:11:55,735
如果我们有办法…
If there was only a way we...

733
01:11:57,346 --> 01:12:01,646
荷姆斯会让你离婚 可是他不会让我请调
Holmes'd give you a divorce, but he'd never let me transfer.

734
01:12:03,686 --> 01:12:05,415
是有一个办法
There is a way.

735
01:12:06,989 --> 01:12:11,221
我一直在考虑这件事 你必须去做军官
I've been thinking about it. You've got to become an officer.

736
01:12:11,427 --> 01:12:16,729
就读新的额外课程 然后他们就会送你回美国
Take the new extension course. Then they'll ship you back to the States.

737
01:12:16,932 --> 01:12:18,866
当军官？
An officer?

738
01:12:19,068 --> 01:12:22,902
是的！这样我可以跟 唐纳离婚再嫁给你
Yes. Then I could divorce Dana and marry you.

739
01:12:23,105 --> 01:12:25,767
我讨厌军官 我一直很讨厌军官
I hate officers! I've always hated them!

740
01:12:26,141 --> 01:12:29,042
那可是个很明智的看法
That's a fine, intelligent point of view.

741
01:12:29,244 --> 01:12:33,874
如果我说我讨厌上士呢？ 这样合理多了
If I said I always hated sergeants? That'd make a lot of sense.

742
01:12:34,083 --> 01:12:36,711
你已经研究得很透澈
You sure made a complete study of it.

743
01:12:38,921 --> 01:12:42,413
好吧！假设我是研究过 别以为这事很容易
Okay, suppose I did. And don't think it's a cinch.

744
01:12:42,624 --> 01:12:46,685
我们必须分开六个月 到时我们一定会参战
We'd be apart six months! We're sure to be in a war by then.

745
01:12:46,895 --> 01:12:50,991
老实说吧！你只是不想负责任
Tell the truth. You just don't want the responsibility.

746
01:12:51,166 --> 01:12:52,861
搞不好你根本不爱我
You probably don't love me.

747
01:12:53,035 --> 01:12:56,994
你疯了！真希望我不爱你 或许我可以再次享受人生
You're crazy! I wish I didn't. Maybe I could enjoy life again.

748
01:13:04,513 --> 01:13:08,244
于是他们结了婚 从此过着不快乐的生活
So, they were married and lived unhappily ever after.

749
01:13:09,885 --> 01:13:13,753
在我遇见你之前 我从不曾如此悲惨
I've never been so miserable as I have since I met you.

750
01:13:14,356 --> 01:13:15,914
我也没有
Neither have I.

751
01:13:16,125 --> 01:13:18,491
我不愿再抛弃一分钟
I wouldn't trade a minute of it.

752
01:13:18,694 --> 01:13:20,457
我也不愿意
Neither would I.

753
01:13:22,231 --> 01:13:26,031
或许我会成为 你见过最差的军官
I'll probably make the lousiest officer you ever saw.

754
01:13:27,002 --> 01:13:29,800
你一定会是个好军官
You'll make a fine officer.

755
01:13:30,005 --> 01:13:32,235
一个很棒的军官
A remarkable officer.

756
01:13:38,013 --> 01:13:39,344
谢谢你
Thank you.

757
01:13:41,450 --> 01:13:43,577
过来
Come here.

758
01:13:46,755 --> 01:13:49,315
难道你不能等我们吃完晚餐？
Can't you wait until we finish dinner?

759
01:13:52,561 --> 01:13:54,620
 亲爱的  什么事？
  Honey.   What?

760
01:13:54,997 --> 01:13:56,589
我想娶你
I want to marry you.

761
01:13:58,834 --> 01:14:00,461
你真是个好玩的家伙
You're a funny one.

762
01:14:00,669 --> 01:14:03,797
为什么有人想娶你 是件好玩的事？
Why is it funny if a guy wants to marry you?

763
01:14:05,274 --> 01:14:08,004
因为你是在 新国会俱乐部认识我
Because you met me at the New Congress Club.

764
01:14:08,210 --> 01:14:10,542
那只不过比最底层高一点而已
That's two steps up from the pavement.

765
01:14:10,746 --> 01:14:14,580
我是什么？不过是个大兵 没有阶级的大兵
Well, what am I? I'm a private, no class dogface.

766
01:14:14,783 --> 01:14:18,719
大部分的人会认为我什么都不是
Most civilians look at that as two steps up from nothing.

767
01:14:20,189 --> 01:14:24,523
我以为我们很快乐 你为何要毁了这一切？
I thought we were happy. Why do you want to spoil things?

768
01:14:24,726 --> 01:14:28,059
听着！我还有一年就要延役
Look, I've got a year to go before I re enlist.

769
01:14:28,764 --> 01:14:32,723
如果到时候我能升为士官 我就可以回美国
If I get sergeant stripes by then, I can go back to the States.

770
01:14:32,935 --> 01:14:35,904
到时我们可以一起回去 如果你愿意等的话
Then we can go back together if you'll wait.

771
01:14:36,104 --> 01:14:39,335
你在荷姆斯手下如何升成士官？
How could you become a sergeant under Holmes?

772
01:14:39,541 --> 01:14:42,669
你只能尽量不被关禁闭
It's all you can do to keep out of the stockade.

773
01:14:45,013 --> 01:14:46,674
我愿意打拳击
I'll fight.

774
01:14:46,882 --> 01:14:49,373
 不，你用不着打拳击  那是值得的
  No, you won't fight.   It'd be worth it.

775
01:14:55,791 --> 01:15:00,728
现在我们彼此是相爱 我们相互需要
It's true we love each other now, we need each other.

776
01:15:01,864 --> 01:15:05,391
但回到美国，就可能大不相同
But back in the States, it might be different.

777
01:15:05,601 --> 01:15:07,569
那不是真正的理由
That ain't the real reason.

778
01:15:10,672 --> 01:15:13,800
 好吧！那不是  什么是真正理由？
  All right, it's not.   What is the real reason?

779
01:15:16,545 --> 01:15:19,844
我不想成为士兵的太太
I don't want to be the wife of a soldier.

780
01:15:25,721 --> 01:15:29,885
我最好只能为你做到那样
That would be about the best I could ever do for you.

781
01:15:32,394 --> 01:15:36,626
因为没有人能妨碍我的计划 没有任何人或任何事
Because nobody'll stop me from my plan. Nobody, nothing.

782
01:15:36,832 --> 01:15:39,892
 因为我想做高尚人  高尚？
  Because I want to be proper.   Proper?

783
01:15:40,102 --> 01:15:41,626
是的，高尚
Yes, proper.

784
01:15:42,738 --> 01:15:45,502
再过一年，我的钱就存够了
In another year, I'll have enough money.

785
01:15:45,707 --> 01:15:50,303
我打算回到奥勒冈 替我妈和自己盖栋房子
Then I'll go back to Oregon and build a house for my mother and myself.

786
01:15:50,512 --> 01:15:53,777
然后加入乡村俱乐部 学打高尔夫球
And join the country club and take up golf.

787
01:15:54,216 --> 01:15:57,777
我会遇到有高尚地位的高尚男士
I'll meet the proper man with the proper position.

788
01:15:58,387 --> 01:16:03,381
我将成为高尚的太太 掌高尚的家，生养高尚的孩子
I'll be a proper wife who can run a proper home and raise proper children.

789
01:16:03,926 --> 01:16:08,158
我会很快乐 因为高尚的人很安全
And I'll be happy because when you're proper, you're safe.

790
01:16:09,798 --> 01:16:11,766
你很有勇气，亲爱的
You got guts, honey.

791
01:16:12,734 --> 01:16:14,929
我希望你能成功
I hope you can pull it off.

792
01:16:23,011 --> 01:16:25,946
当我说需要你时是真心的
I do mean it when I say I need you.

793
01:16:26,148 --> 01:16:27,809
因为我很寂寞
Because I'm lonely.

794
01:16:29,284 --> 01:16:31,275
你认为我在说谎，对吧？
You think I'm lying, don't you?

795
01:16:32,821 --> 01:16:35,619
没有人会用寂寞来说谎话
Nobody ever lies about being lonely.

796
01:16:44,533 --> 01:16:46,558
不要跟我提离婚的事
Don't talk to me about a divorce.

797
01:16:46,768 --> 01:16:51,068
为什么？难道丑闻会 破坏你升迁的机会？
Why? Because the scandal would spoil your chances for a promotion?

798
01:16:51,273 --> 01:16:54,436
我要知道对方是谁 以及你是在哪里认识他的
I want to know who he is and where you met him.

799
01:16:54,643 --> 01:16:56,338
我绝对不会告诉你
I'm not going to tell you.

800
01:16:57,713 --> 01:17:02,776
我知道他是个老百姓 你谨慎的不会找军人
I know he's a civilian. You'd be too discreet to pick an Army man.

801
01:17:02,985 --> 01:17:06,045
我不知道是你的骄傲 还是你的好奇让我重伤？
I wonder which is hurt more, your pride or your curiosity?

802
01:17:06,254 --> 01:17:08,279
你不会知道我的感受
You can't expect to know how I feel.

803
01:17:08,490 --> 01:17:11,618
为什么男人的感觉如此不同？
Why do men feel so differently about it?

804
01:17:11,827 --> 01:17:14,261
根本完全不一样
It's just not the same.

805
01:17:19,067 --> 01:17:22,127
今天天气真好，我想去散个步
It's a lovely day. I think I'll go for a walk.

806
01:17:29,077 --> 01:17:31,841
我听说你才关完禁闭出来
I hear you just got out of the stockade.

807
01:17:32,414 --> 01:17:35,383
那里真的很难捱 我不想再多说
It was rugged. I kept my mouth shut.

808
01:17:35,584 --> 01:17:39,714
 你有见到马吉欧吗？  胖子把马吉欧折磨得很惨
  Did you see Maggio?   Fatso's really got it in for Maggio.

809
01:17:39,921 --> 01:17:41,718
他甚至用了警棍
He's using a billy, too.

810
01:17:42,157 --> 01:17:45,991
专打看不到的地方 比如说背后或胸前
In places where it won't show. On the back, on the chest.

811
01:17:46,194 --> 01:17:49,891
他甚至有个系统 他还经常踢他
He's got it down to a system. He kicks him a lot too.

812
01:17:50,932 --> 01:17:53,127
你知道马吉欧的反应如何？
You know how Maggio's taking it?

813
01:17:53,335 --> 01:17:56,099
他一直对胖子吐口水
He just keeps spitting in Fatso's eye.

814
01:17:56,972 --> 01:17:58,439
他真有个性，是吗？
Ain't he a hot one?

815
01:17:59,975 --> 01:18:01,636
他是一个好人
He's a good man.

816
01:18:03,478 --> 01:18:08,245
老胖子伤不了他 那个胖子是个聪明人
Old Fatso can't make a dent in him. That Fatso, he's smart.

817
01:18:08,450 --> 01:18:12,409
 值星官从来看不到什么的  为什么马吉欧不向值星官报告？
  The OD never sees nothing.   Why don't Maggio go to the OD?

818
01:18:12,621 --> 01:18:17,115
我们曾鼓励他去报告但他不肯 他真的很倔强
We tried to get him to, but he won't peep. He's a tough nut.

819
01:18:17,592 --> 01:18:19,753
你认为他能平安吗？
You think he'll be all right?

820
01:18:20,462 --> 01:18:23,124
 他可能快崩溃了  这话什么意思？
  Maybe he's cracking.   What do you mean?

821
01:18:23,665 --> 01:18:26,725
胖子将他关进洞里，就是 单人牢房后…
After Fatso threw him in the hole... that's solitary...

822
01:18:26,935 --> 01:18:29,961
他开始不停地说他要如何逃跑
...he started talking about how he'll escape.

823
01:18:30,706 --> 01:18:33,573
他说他某个晚上会来找你
He said he'll look you up one of these nights.

824
01:18:35,510 --> 01:18:37,876
你还趴在地上吗？普威特
Still on your knees, Prewitt?

825
01:18:38,447 --> 01:18:41,780
拳击决赛在下个月 十二月十五日
Boxing finals next month. December 15th.

826
01:18:41,983 --> 01:18:44,952
你还有时间帮我们赢得冠军
Still time to help us win the championship.

827
01:18:47,222 --> 01:18:50,385
你是否以加入本军团为荣？
Are you proud to be in this company or not?

828
01:18:57,999 --> 01:19:02,868
 我不会再绕过你了  看来你需要点教训
  I won't move around you again.   Something tells me you need a lesson.

829
01:19:03,071 --> 01:19:05,631
或许我会亲自教训你
Maybe I'll give it to you myself.

830
01:19:09,344 --> 01:19:13,781
别惹他！他是我小队上的人 如果你打架，麻烦可就大了
Leave him alone, he's in my detail. You'll get in trouble if you fight.

831
01:19:13,982 --> 01:19:16,075
 回去工作  别挡路
  Get back to work.   Get out of the way!

832
01:19:46,848 --> 01:19:48,839
我很乐意提供推荐信
I'll be glad to give my recommendation.

833
01:19:49,050 --> 01:19:51,109
你有功绩，经验和官阶
You've got service, experience, grade.

834
01:19:51,319 --> 01:19:53,753
 你一定会成为好军官  谢谢你，长官
  You'll make an excellent officer.   Thank you, sir.

835
01:19:53,955 --> 01:19:57,152
军团里能有你这种人 也是值得让我骄傲的事
A feather in my cap too. A man from my company.

836
01:19:59,561 --> 01:20:01,153
出了什么事？
What's the trouble?

837
01:20:01,530 --> 01:20:05,466
葛罗维奇和普威特 他们在外头打架，长官
They're fighting outside, sir. Galovitch and Prewitt.

838
01:20:05,667 --> 01:20:08,135
葛罗维奇会杀了他，长官
Galovitch's going to murder him, sir.

839
01:20:08,336 --> 01:20:09,860
我会处理
I'll take care of it.

840
01:20:14,743 --> 01:20:18,611
 难道你不想看吗？  不想！你也别看！出去
  Don't you want to see?   No! Nor you, either! Get out!

841
01:20:26,888 --> 01:20:30,915
 为什么普威特不打他的头？  他曾打瞎某个人所以很害怕
  Why don't Prew go for his head?   He blinded a guy once, he's scared.

842
01:20:39,401 --> 01:20:41,266
揍他的脸
Hit him in the face!

843
01:21:00,856 --> 01:21:04,849
 拜托！葛罗维奇！公平竞赛！  我想怎么打都行
  Come on, Galovitch, fight fair!   I'll fight any way I want.

844
01:21:40,328 --> 01:21:43,491
那位军官应该阻止这场架 他叫什么名字？
That officer should stop the fight. What's his name?

845
01:21:43,698 --> 01:21:45,461
荷姆斯上尉，长官
Captain Holmes, sir.

846
01:22:14,596 --> 01:22:16,621
稍息！是谁先动手的？
At ease. What started this?

847
01:22:16,831 --> 01:22:18,731
普威特违抗我给他的命令
Prewitt refused order I gave him.

848
01:22:18,934 --> 01:22:23,098
开始顶嘴并且挑衅 所以我才会教训他
Talked back and started a fight. I taught him a lesson.

849
01:22:23,305 --> 01:22:25,136
你不可以再抗命
You won't disobey any more orders.

850
01:22:25,340 --> 01:22:30,107
长官！这件事不能怪普威特 是葛罗维奇上士起头的
I'm sorry, sir, but Prewitt's not to blame. Sergeant Galovitch started it.

851
01:22:30,445 --> 01:22:34,006
索希尔，这个小队是你带的 到底怎么回事？
Thornhill. You're in charge of this detail. What about it?

852
01:22:34,215 --> 01:22:38,208
 他说得对，普威特没有犯错  是葛罗维奇起的头
  He's right. Prewitt did nothing.   Galovitch started it.

853
01:22:39,187 --> 01:22:43,214
够了！这事算了 回去做自己的工作
That's all. Let's forget it. Let's get back to our jobs.

854
01:22:43,892 --> 01:22:46,918
好了！回去工作 动作快！解散
All right, back to work. Let's go. Break it up.

855
01:22:50,298 --> 01:22:53,461
如果你认为这样我就会出赛 你就错了
If you think this means I'll fight, you're wrong.

856
01:22:53,668 --> 01:22:56,228
你的伤口最好擦点碘酒
You'd better put some iodine on them cuts.

857
01:23:39,481 --> 01:23:43,349
星期五，你怎么会叫星期五？
Hey, Friday. Why're you called "Friday"?

858
01:23:43,551 --> 01:23:46,714
我也不知道 我是在星期三生的
I don't know. I was born on a Wednesday.

859
01:24:56,057 --> 01:24:58,287
普威特，你要去哪里？
Prewitt, where are you going?

860
01:24:58,493 --> 01:25:02,930
什么意思？我要去裘伊酒吧 再多买罐啤酒
What do you mean? I'm going to Choy's to get me another beer.

861
01:25:17,145 --> 01:25:18,442
别动！
Halt!

862
01:25:20,381 --> 01:25:21,939
谁在那里？
Who goes there?

863
01:25:22,784 --> 01:25:26,345
 一个朋友  朋友，请你上前表明身份
  A friend.   Advance, friend, and be recognized!

864
01:25:36,097 --> 01:25:37,962
立正！
Ten hut!

865
01:25:38,366 --> 01:25:41,233
向后转！向后转走！
About face! Rear face!

866
01:25:41,436 --> 01:25:44,462
跪下！刷地板
On your knees! Scrub the floor!

867
01:25:44,973 --> 01:25:46,531
稍息
At ease.

868
01:25:49,110 --> 01:25:52,876
小子，你一个人在这做什么？
Hello, kid. What you doing out here all by yourself?

869
01:25:55,350 --> 01:25:59,286
 我去买酒  坐下！我还有一瓶
  I'm getting a little drink.   Sit down. I got a bottle.

870
01:26:06,127 --> 01:26:07,617
谢谢，军士长
Thanks, top.

871
01:26:09,330 --> 01:26:13,664
我一定得称赞你 揍葛罗维奇的方法，小子
I got to hand it to you, kid, the way you beat up old Galovitch.

872
01:26:14,035 --> 01:26:17,163
可惜他们迟早会扳倒你
Too bad they got to get you sooner or later.

873
01:26:25,079 --> 01:26:27,604
生命就是这么烂，你知道吗？
Life's crummy, you know it?

874
01:26:27,815 --> 01:26:31,478
是的，长官，是很悲惨 非常地悲惨
Yes, sir, it's miserable, perfectly miserable.

875
01:26:33,021 --> 01:26:37,287
如果现在有辆卡车 开过来撞上我们怎么办？
What would happen if a truck came along and ran us over?

876
01:26:38,526 --> 01:26:41,962
 我们就死定了  你最好别再坐在这里
  We'd be dead.   You better not sit here anymore.

877
01:26:42,163 --> 01:26:44,529
起来坐到路旁去
Get up and sit over on the side.

878
01:26:44,732 --> 01:26:47,030
你在说什么？我…可是…
What do you mean, I? But...

879
01:26:47,302 --> 01:26:51,830
你比我更需要活下去 你还得照顾整个军团
You've got more to live for than me, a whole company to take care of.

880
01:26:52,006 --> 01:26:54,236
你快移到路旁
You move over to the other side.

881
01:26:54,442 --> 01:26:56,933
我年纪比较大，死了没关系
I'm older, it don't matter if I die.

882
01:26:57,145 --> 01:26:59,705
现在别争了！快点起来
Now, don't argue. Go on, get up.

883
01:26:59,914 --> 01:27:04,851
不！长官！普威特不去 普威特决定待到苦果的最后
No, sir, not Prewitt. Prewitt stays right here to the bitter end.

884
01:27:07,088 --> 01:27:10,319
好吧！我们一起留在这里
Okay, we'll stay together.

885
01:27:13,861 --> 01:27:16,830
反正我也站不起来
I couldn't have got up anyway.

886
01:27:21,102 --> 01:27:24,230
我惹了世界上最大的麻烦
I got the biggest troubles in the whole world.

887
01:27:25,273 --> 01:27:27,138
世界级的吗？
In the whole world, huh?

888
01:27:27,809 --> 01:27:29,470
都是因为爱
Take love.

889
01:27:30,078 --> 01:27:33,275
你曾经见过爱情吗？
Did you personally ever see any of this love?

890
01:27:33,748 --> 01:27:37,980
你不明白我的意思 这个女孩…
You don't understand what I mean. This girl, see...

891
01:27:38,553 --> 01:27:40,817
她要求我成为…
...she wants me to become...

892
01:27:41,789 --> 01:27:43,814
 成为什么？  一名军官
  Become what?   An officer.

893
01:27:44,025 --> 01:27:46,755
你能想像我当军官的样子吗？
Can you see me as an officer?

894
01:27:47,562 --> 01:27:51,430
可以！我能想像你当军官 你一定会是个好军官
Yeah, I can see you as an officer. You'd be a good officer.

895
01:27:51,633 --> 01:27:54,568
你们两个比我有远见
You both can see more than I can see.

896
01:27:54,769 --> 01:27:58,170
我不想当军官 我很喜欢现在这样
I don't want to be an officer. I'm happy where I am.

897
01:28:00,375 --> 01:28:02,866
搞不好我会变成荷姆斯那种人
I might turn out to be a guy like Holmes.

898
01:28:03,478 --> 01:28:06,504
你不希望我跟荷姆斯一样吧？
You wouldn't want me to be like Holmes, would you?

899
01:28:08,349 --> 01:28:10,010
你会吗？
Well, would you?

900
01:28:11,319 --> 01:28:13,947
男人应该做自己在行的事
A man should be what he can do.

901
01:28:25,433 --> 01:28:30,097
你的女朋友呢？ 再告诉我一次她的芳名
How's your girl? What's her name again?

902
01:28:32,106 --> 01:28:35,439
 萝琳  对了！就是萝琳
  Lorene.   Oh, yeah, Lorene.

903
01:28:35,643 --> 01:28:39,943
我现在想起来了 好美的名字
I remember now. Beautiful name.

904
01:28:40,848 --> 01:28:42,213
美极了
Beautiful.

905
01:28:48,022 --> 01:28:50,217
你们两个愚蠢的疯家伙
You two dumb, crazy screwballs.

906
01:28:50,425 --> 01:28:54,156
你们想找死吗？ 你们在这里做什么？
You trying to get killed? What're you doing here?

907
01:28:54,362 --> 01:28:57,798
我的朋友普威特跟我 坐在这里讨论天气
My friend Prew and I are sitting here discussing the weather.

908
01:28:57,999 --> 01:28:59,967
你的朋友？
Your friend, huh?

909
01:29:00,168 --> 01:29:02,762
你得好好照顾这个人
You got to take care of this man.

910
01:29:02,970 --> 01:29:06,030
荷姆斯迟早会整倒他
Holmes is bound to get him sooner or later.

911
01:29:06,240 --> 01:29:08,868
他是陆军最棒的士兵
And he's the best soldier in the Army.

912
01:29:09,077 --> 01:29:11,637
你们两个都晕头了
You both got rocks in your head.

913
01:29:15,850 --> 01:29:17,909
安杰罗！安杰罗
Angelo, Angelo!

914
01:29:21,255 --> 01:29:24,019
我就知道你一定在裘伊酒吧
I figured you'd be here at Choy's.

915
01:29:26,027 --> 01:29:27,494
我办到了！普威特
I done it, Prew.

916
01:29:27,695 --> 01:29:31,461
正如我所说的，我逃出来了 跟我所计划的一样
I escaped, just like I said. Just like I figured.

917
01:29:31,766 --> 01:29:34,633
跳上了卡车，躲在防水布下面
In a back of a truck, under a tarp.

918
01:29:35,036 --> 01:29:38,836
跟我所计划的一样 他们开车把我也载了出来
They rode me right out, just like I figured.

919
01:29:39,607 --> 01:29:44,704
可惜离这儿一哩后，后挡泥板 就掉了，所以我跌到路上
Only the tailgate opened up about a mile back, and I fell out in the road.

920
01:29:45,947 --> 01:29:50,179
你应该看我弹跳的样子 我应该有骨折才对
You should've seen me bounce. I must've broke something.

921
01:29:56,424 --> 01:29:58,051
普威特，听我说
Prew, listen.

922
01:29:58,659 --> 01:30:00,627
胖子做的，普威特
Fatso done it, Prew.

923
01:30:00,828 --> 01:30:02,921
他很喜欢修理我
He likes to whack me in the gut.

924
01:30:03,331 --> 01:30:07,927
一如往常，他问我会不会痛 然后我直接对着他吐口水
He asks me if it hurts and I spit at him like always.

925
01:30:08,136 --> 01:30:11,663
只是昨天，情况很糟
Only yesterday, it was bad.

926
01:30:11,906 --> 01:30:16,502
他不断的打我
He hit me, he hit me, he hit me.

927
01:30:17,879 --> 01:30:21,679
我一定要出来，普威特 我一定要出来
I had to get out, Prew, I had to get out.

928
01:30:23,184 --> 01:30:26,381
 他们会送你回禁闭室  不，他们不会
  They'll send you to the stockade.   No, they won't.

929
01:30:26,587 --> 01:30:30,614
小心胖子！要小心胖子
Watch out for Fatso. Watch out for Fatso.

930
01:30:30,825 --> 01:30:32,520
他想要修理你
He'll try to crack you.

931
01:30:32,727 --> 01:30:34,991
如果他们把你关进单人牢里
If they put you in the hole...

932
01:30:35,229 --> 01:30:38,858
千万别大叫，不要出声
...don't yell, don't make a sound.

933
01:30:39,367 --> 01:30:43,064
否则当他们把你拉出来时 你还是在叫
You'll still be yelling when they come to take you out.

934
01:30:43,471 --> 01:30:45,268
你只管躺在那里
Just lay there...

935
01:30:45,640 --> 01:30:50,009
安安静静地躺在那里，普威特
...just lay there and be quiet, Prew.

936
01:31:04,125 --> 01:31:05,717
他死了
He's dead.

937
01:31:36,357 --> 01:31:38,484
我打赌那一定是普威特
I'll bet you that's Prew.

938
01:34:00,835 --> 01:34:02,530
贾德森上士
Sergeant Judson?

939
01:34:03,537 --> 01:34:05,061
你找我吗？
You want me?

940
01:34:05,740 --> 01:34:07,230
是的，胖子
Yeah, Fatso.

941
01:34:07,775 --> 01:34:12,075
我不喜欢那个外号 你找我有什么事吗？
I don't like that nickname. You want to see me about something?

942
01:34:12,747 --> 01:34:15,807
我们找个角落好好谈谈
Let's step around the corner where we can talk.

943
01:34:28,929 --> 01:34:30,897
你在生气什么吗？
Are you sore about something?

944
01:34:31,532 --> 01:34:34,330
我不喜欢你弹琴的方式
I don't like the way you play the piano.

945
01:34:36,303 --> 01:34:40,603
 还记得马吉欧吗？  意大利佬？记得！那个泼猴
  Remember Maggio?   The wop? Yeah, real tough monkey.

946
01:34:40,808 --> 01:34:43,333
 你杀了他  我有吗？
  You killed him.   Did I?

947
01:34:43,544 --> 01:34:45,603
如果我有，也是他咎由自取
If I did, he asked for it.

948
01:34:45,813 --> 01:34:48,873
军队迟早会惩罚你
The Army's going to get you sooner or later.

949
01:34:49,083 --> 01:34:52,280
可是在他们动手之前 我想先找你算算帐
But before they do, I want a piece of you myself.

950
01:34:54,121 --> 01:34:55,679
我早知道了
I figured that.

951
01:34:56,624 --> 01:35:00,720
看到这把刀了吗？ 是你先前威胁马吉欧时所用的
See this knife? It's the one you pulled on Maggio.

952
01:36:36,991 --> 01:36:38,652
出了什么事？
What's happened?

953
01:36:44,799 --> 01:36:46,061
没事了
It's all right.

954
01:36:48,836 --> 01:36:52,567
别担心！别担心！我死不了
Don't worry. Don't worry. I ain't going to die.

955
01:37:02,416 --> 01:37:07,820
仍然不知道谋杀 警卫上士的凶手是谁

956
01:37:10,357 --> 01:37:11,915
全数到齐
All present and accounted for!

957
01:37:12,126 --> 01:37:13,855
全数到齐
All present and accounted for!

958
01:37:14,061 --> 01:37:16,120
全数到齐
All present and accounted for!

959
01:37:16,330 --> 01:37:18,321
全数到齐
All present and accounted for!

960
01:37:18,899 --> 01:37:20,560
全数到齐
All present and accounted for!

961
01:37:20,768 --> 01:37:22,326
全数到齐
All present and accounted for!

962
01:37:22,970 --> 01:37:26,133
队伍解散
Company dismissed!

963
01:37:30,678 --> 01:37:32,373
普威特还是没有出席
Prewitt's still absent.

964
01:37:33,681 --> 01:37:35,615
已经三天了
Makes three days now.

965
01:37:38,085 --> 01:37:40,781
你还要替他瞒多久？
How long will you carry him present?

966
01:37:41,655 --> 01:37:44,556
 我只是说说  那么就别再说了
  I just mention it.   Well, don't mention it.

967
01:37:49,396 --> 01:37:50,693
将军室

968
01:37:51,699 --> 01:37:54,691
督察长展开调查…
"Upon these incidents, an investigation was made...

969
01:37:54,902 --> 01:37:58,565
这些事件数个月
...by the inspector general over several months.

970
01:37:58,772 --> 01:38:02,572
发现荷姆斯上尉 对普威特士兵残酷的罪行
Captain Holmes was found guilty of indefensible cruelty...

971
01:38:02,776 --> 01:38:04,471
是无可辩解的
...to Private Prewitt.

972
01:38:04,678 --> 01:38:08,580
其中包括唆使运用 未经许可的方式
This included the instigation of unauthorized tactics...

973
01:38:08,782 --> 01:38:12,582
意图强迫他参加军团拳击赛
...to force him to join the inter regiment boxing team."

974
01:38:18,158 --> 01:38:21,992
 我正在等你回答  我无话可说，长官
  I'm waiting for your reply.   I haven't any, sir.

975
01:38:22,363 --> 01:38:25,457
荷姆斯，我在军队中 学习到的第一件事
Holmes, the first thing I learned in the Army...

976
01:38:25,666 --> 01:38:28,294
就是军官要好好照顾部属
...was that an officer takes care of his men.

977
01:38:28,502 --> 01:38:31,198
但这似乎是你最早忘记的事
It seems to be the first thing you forgot.

978
01:38:31,405 --> 01:38:34,169
我很遗憾必须让你保留军职
I regret that we have to keep you in uniform...

979
01:38:34,375 --> 01:38:36,741
直到军事法庭做出判决
...until a court martial is concluded.

980
01:38:36,944 --> 01:38:40,573
若有办法能免除上军事法庭…
If there were any way to avoid a court martial, sir...

981
01:38:40,915 --> 01:38:44,646
如果你愿意的话，将军 我倒有另一项选择
There is one alternative, general, if you are so disposed.

982
01:38:44,852 --> 01:38:49,448
依照陆军规定辞职
A resignation for the good of the service under Army regulations.

983
01:38:50,157 --> 01:38:54,025
下午就提出辞呈
Write a letter of resignation for this afternoon.

984
01:38:54,228 --> 01:38:58,688
你愈快离开陆军 对大家愈有利
The quicker you're out of the Army, the better for everybody.

985
01:38:58,899 --> 01:39:01,026
尤其是对陆军
Especially the Army.

986
01:39:02,569 --> 01:39:04,400
就这样决定，荷姆斯
That's all, Holmes.

987
01:39:12,046 --> 01:39:16,710
我很清楚事情的发展 也知道你有多么过份
I know what's been going on, how far some of you have been out of line.

988
01:39:17,084 --> 01:39:20,019
如果你还想继任无委任状士官 就得赶紧努力
If you want to remain non coms, snap into it.

989
01:39:20,220 --> 01:39:25,283
从现在开始 拳击已无法替任何人赢得官阶
From now on, no man's going to earn his stripes by boxing.

990
01:39:27,928 --> 01:39:30,158
 把那些扔掉  是的，长官
  Get rid of those.   Yes, sir.

991
01:39:30,464 --> 01:39:31,954
解散！
Dismissed.

992
01:39:38,038 --> 01:39:40,063
 关于葛罗维奇上士  是的，长官
  About Sergeant Galovitch.   Yes, sir.

993
01:39:40,274 --> 01:39:43,004
将他降级为葛罗维奇大兵
Bust him. He is now Private Galovitch.

994
01:39:43,210 --> 01:39:47,203
派他去管厕所 你在笑什么？
Put him in charge of the latrine. What are you grinning at?

995
01:39:47,414 --> 01:39:50,542
军团连长做了明智决定
The company commander made a wise decision, sir.

996
01:39:52,920 --> 01:39:55,115
参谋部，罗斯上尉
Company G, Captain Ross.

997
01:39:56,690 --> 01:39:58,555
请等一下！你的电话
Just a minute. It's for you.

998
01:39:58,759 --> 01:40:00,249
谢谢你，长官
Thank you, sir.

999
01:40:03,697 --> 01:40:05,062
是的，长官
Yes, sir.

1000
01:40:07,968 --> 01:40:11,404
是的，包裹已经到了
Yes, the parcel has already arrived.

1001
01:40:12,006 --> 01:40:13,268
什么？
What?

1002
01:40:13,440 --> 01:40:15,738
我必须见你一面 这件事很重要
I've got to see you. It's important.

1003
01:40:19,279 --> 01:40:22,976
好的，我想办法去 当然，没有问题
Okay, I'll get away somehow. Sure, that'd be fine.

1004
01:40:24,585 --> 01:40:26,746
我一小时之内赶到
I'll be there in about an hour.

1005
01:40:31,158 --> 01:40:33,251
他下礼拜就要被送回去
He's being sent back next week.

1006
01:40:33,460 --> 01:40:36,452
他要我跟他一起走 我们怎么办？
He wants me to go with him. What'll we do?

1007
01:40:38,699 --> 01:40:41,167
你何时能拿到派令？
When will you get your commission?

1008
01:40:44,705 --> 01:40:48,801
我没有申请 我是填好了但并没有签名
I didn't put it in. I filled it out, but I didn't sign it.

1009
01:40:49,009 --> 01:40:52,604
我把它拿出来许多次 但就是无法签名
I took it out a dozen times, but I couldn't sign it.

1010
01:40:53,447 --> 01:40:54,937
为什么？
Why?

1011
01:40:56,150 --> 01:40:58,778
 这是我们的计划  我知道…
  But it was the plan.   I know, I know.

1012
01:40:58,986 --> 01:41:02,547
你不能光说不做
You can't just say you'll do a thing and then not do it.

1013
01:41:02,756 --> 01:41:04,053
凯伦，听我说
Karen, listen to me.

1014
01:41:04,258 --> 01:41:07,352
你为什么不申请？ 你为什么不告诉我？
Why didn't you do it? Why didn't you tell me?

1015
01:41:08,829 --> 01:41:10,490
我马上回来
Be back in a minute.

1016
01:41:13,133 --> 01:41:16,034
对不起，我以为你是某人
Sorry, I thought you were somebody else.

1017
01:41:22,209 --> 01:41:25,542
我以为是我们军团的普威特
I thought it was that kid Prewitt from our company.

1018
01:41:25,746 --> 01:41:28,476
他迷上俱乐部的女孩
He got mixed up with a girl at the club.

1019
01:41:28,682 --> 01:41:31,378
他不假外出，可能有大麻烦
He's AWOL, probably in lots of trouble.

1020
01:41:31,985 --> 01:41:35,113
罗勃普威特是个疯狂的坏家伙
Robert E. Lee Prewitt, a crazy, no good...

1021
01:41:38,025 --> 01:41:41,722
凯伦，我不是当军官的料 我是个军人
Karen, I'm no officer. I'm an enlisted man.

1022
01:41:41,895 --> 01:41:45,194
别的事我都做不来 我一定只会装装样子
I can't be anything else. I'd be putting on an act.

1023
01:41:45,399 --> 01:41:48,562
我就是办不到 请不要问我原因
I just can't do it. Please don't ask me why.

1024
01:41:50,838 --> 01:41:52,601
我知道原因
I know why.

1025
01:41:53,273 --> 01:41:57,972
因为现在唐纳已经离开军队 所以你用不着去当军官
You don't have to become an officer now that Dana's out of the Army.

1026
01:41:58,212 --> 01:42:00,578
你就是不想娶我
You just don't want to marry me.

1027
01:42:00,781 --> 01:42:03,306
你已经结了婚 娶了陆军
You're already married. To the Army.

1028
01:42:03,517 --> 01:42:05,246
我是爱你的，凯伦
I love you, Karen.

1029
01:42:10,824 --> 01:42:12,951
我知道…
I know. I know.

1030
01:42:15,129 --> 01:42:19,566
 我不希望你回到他身边  我也不想但我是在他身边
  I don't want you to go back to him.   I don't want to, either, but I am.

1031
01:42:19,766 --> 01:42:22,132
我已经无能为力
There's nothing else for me to do.

1032
01:42:22,336 --> 01:42:25,362
对我们并没有好处 从来不可能有好结果
It's no good with us. It could never have been.

1033
01:42:25,572 --> 01:42:29,167
这样东躲西藏 磨耗了我们的感情
The hiding and the sneaking. It had to wear out.

1034
01:42:33,013 --> 01:42:34,537
再见了，上士
Goodbye, sergeant.

1035
01:42:35,349 --> 01:42:37,874
 谢谢  这不是再见而是…
  Thanks.   It ain't goodbye, it's...

1036
01:42:39,153 --> 01:42:41,986
总有一天我们会再某处重逢
We'll see each other again, somewhere.

1037
01:42:42,789 --> 01:42:44,689
我们当然会
Of course we will.

1038
01:42:44,892 --> 01:42:46,519
就在某处
Somewhere.

1039
01:43:00,607 --> 01:43:04,407
有消息了！已经登在内页
Here it is. They got it on the inside page already.

1040
01:43:05,112 --> 01:43:10,049
“谋杀詹姆士贾德森上士凶手 至今仍毫无线索”
"Still no clue in the fatal stabbing of Staff Sergeant James R. Judson."

1041
01:43:10,717 --> 01:43:12,412
你听见我说的吗？
Did you hear me?

1042
01:43:15,589 --> 01:43:18,456
你想创下新世界纪录吗？
You trying to set a new world's record?

1043
01:43:20,194 --> 01:43:23,027
是的，我就是这么打算
Yeah, as a matter of fact, I am.

1044
01:43:23,830 --> 01:43:26,355
纪念罗勃普威特
To the memory of Robert E. Lee Prewitt...

1045
01:43:26,800 --> 01:43:29,769
新世界纪录保持人
...holder of the new world's record.

1046
01:43:45,986 --> 01:43:48,716
 还好吗？军士长  好极了
  Everything all right, top?   Great.

1047
01:43:49,189 --> 01:43:54,525
这是在星期天的一顿美味餐 恭喜你了
A beautiful meal to put in front of a guy on Sunday. Congratulations.

1048
01:44:08,375 --> 01:44:12,141
 从山上看下去真美  说得也是？
  They look pretty over the mountains.   Don't they?

1049
01:44:21,255 --> 01:44:23,883
他们要轰炸车轮草原吗？
Are they dynamiting Wheeler Field?

1050
01:44:24,091 --> 01:44:28,084
真是有野心，是吧？ 星期天早上还不到八点钟
Mighty ambitious, huh? Sunday morning before 8:00.

1051
01:44:40,173 --> 01:44:43,540
日本战机正在轰炸车轮草原
The Japs are bombing Wheeler Field!

1052
01:44:43,744 --> 01:44:46,713
我看到红圆圈…
I seen the red circles on the...

1053
01:45:17,110 --> 01:45:19,772
到里面去！快一点！
Get inside! Hurry up, go!

1054
01:45:23,950 --> 01:45:28,410
这是真的，不是演习 日本人正在轰炸珍珠港
<i>This is real, not a maneuver.</i> <i>The Japanese are bombing Pearl Harbor.</i>

1055
01:45:28,622 --> 01:45:30,988
请留在室内！不要任意外出
<i>Keep in your homes. Do not go out.</i>

1056
01:45:31,191 --> 01:45:36,288
日本战正在轰炸 我方的海军及陆军设施
<i>Japanese planes are bombing</i> <i>our Naval and Army installations.</i>

1057
01:45:37,497 --> 01:45:41,627
好了！各位！安静！安静下来
All right, you guys, quiet down. Quiet. Quiet down!

1058
01:45:41,902 --> 01:45:45,861
士官们，快去拿机关枪和弹药 然后到屋顶上去
Non coms, get B A Rs and ammunition and get up on the roof.

1059
01:45:46,073 --> 01:45:50,442
韩德生，你负责装填子弹 动作快一点
Henderson, you're in charge of the loading detail. Get moving.

1060
01:45:50,844 --> 01:45:55,281
其他人快去拿步枪 然后回卧铺去，留在那里别动
The rest of you, get your rifle, go to your bunk and stay there.

1061
01:45:55,482 --> 01:45:57,609
我要你们留在那里
And I mean stay there!

1062
01:45:58,652 --> 01:46:00,517
闭嘴！
Shut up!

1063
01:46:00,921 --> 01:46:04,914
你们到外面会被击中 你们有机会成为英雄
You'll be shot outside! You'll get a chance to be heroes.

1064
01:46:05,125 --> 01:46:09,528
在夜晚来临之前 日本人就会坐在你的大腿上！快
There'll be Japs in your lap before night. Now get moving!

1065
01:46:12,599 --> 01:46:17,696
去煮一壶咖啡 等一下！煮一桶咖啡
Go make a pot of coffee. Wait a minute, a barrel of coffee!

1066
01:46:38,225 --> 01:46:40,693
没有命令我不能发给弹药
I can't issue ammo without an order.

1067
01:46:40,894 --> 01:46:43,761
 可是上尉不在营里  很抱歉
  But the captain ain't here!   I'm sorry.

1068
01:46:43,964 --> 01:46:48,799
 怎么回事？列瓦  我奉命如此！陆军规定…
  What's the matter, Leva?   I got orders! Army regulations say...

1069
01:46:53,173 --> 01:46:56,074
 你瞎了吗？把钥匙拿来  我奉命如此
  You blind? Give me the keys!   I got orders!

1070
01:46:56,276 --> 01:47:00,007
 我会看着你得到勋章！冲开  我警告过你
  I'll see you get a medal! Bust it.   I warned you!

1071
01:47:23,503 --> 01:47:28,236
 别出去！你会没命的  快点穿衣服！你会着凉的
  Don't go out there! You'll die!   Get dressed. You'll catch cold.

1072
01:47:55,068 --> 01:47:58,902
快帮他们处理弹药 把那个东西放在那边
Help them with this ammo! Put that stuff over there.

1073
01:48:04,311 --> 01:48:07,280
小心开火！瞄准飞机前方
Watch your fire and lead those planes!

1074
01:48:27,567 --> 01:48:30,092
他正在吹“骑兵突袭乐”
He's blowing the "Cavalry Charge"!

1075
01:48:33,673 --> 01:48:35,698
他们来了！各位
Here they come, boys!

1076
01:49:06,940 --> 01:49:09,932
 我打中他了！我打中他了  我打中他了
  I got him! I got him!   I got him.

1077
01:49:18,919 --> 01:49:21,387
入侵的危机仍然存在
<i>The danger of invasion still exists.</i>

1078
01:49:21,588 --> 01:49:26,616
雪菲德部队在数小时内移防 并已就滩头位置
<i>Schofield units moved out within hours</i> <i>and have manned beach positions.</i>

1079
01:49:26,826 --> 01:49:30,557
这不是演习！这是真正打仗
<i>This is no maneuver.</i> <i>This is the real McCoy.</i>

1080
01:49:30,764 --> 01:49:33,961
小心榴霰弹！快找掩护
<i>Look out for falling shrapnel.</i> <i>Keep under cover.</i>

1081
01:49:34,167 --> 01:49:37,864
将实施灯火管制及宵禁
<i>Blackout and curfew restrictions</i> <i>will be enforced.</i>

1082
01:49:38,071 --> 01:49:41,006
请留在家中并不要使用电话
<i>Stay in your homes.</i> <i>Don't use the phone.</i>

1083
01:49:42,275 --> 01:49:44,766
我们传播所有资讯…
<i>We'll relay all information...</i>

1084
01:49:46,179 --> 01:49:48,010
我们捐血了
We've been giving blood.

1085
01:49:48,214 --> 01:49:51,308
 简直混乱极了  库希欧有房子遭到轰炸
  It's a madhouse!   A house got bombed on Kuhio.

1086
01:49:51,518 --> 01:49:55,614
一间杂货店被夷为平地 有对夫妇因而丧生
And a drugstore smashed flat! A man and his wife were killed.

1087
01:49:55,822 --> 01:50:00,122
请各位注意 注意听好并保持镇静
<i>Your attention, please.</i> <i>Listen carefully and keep calm.</i>

1088
01:50:00,327 --> 01:50:03,524
入侵的危机仍然存在
<i>The danger of invasion still exists.</i>

1089
01:50:03,730 --> 01:50:07,564
进行轰炸的飞机 已确认属日方所有
<i>And the planes have been</i> <i>identified as Japanese...</i>

1090
01:50:08,234 --> 01:50:10,702
他们以为在向谁挑衅？
Who do they think they're fighting?

1091
01:50:10,904 --> 01:50:14,340
他们正在对抗 世界上最精良的陆军
They're fighting the best Army in the world.

1092
01:50:15,709 --> 01:50:19,475
 你要上哪儿去？  我必须回去…
  Where are you going?   I gotta get back to...

1093
01:50:19,679 --> 01:50:24,139
 我必须回部队去  部队？为什么？
  I gotta get back to the company.   The company? But why?

1094
01:50:24,351 --> 01:50:28,549
 为什么？  不可以！你还没有复原
  Why?   But you can't. You're not well yet.

1095
01:50:28,755 --> 01:50:31,451
你会被关到禁闭室
And you'll be thrown in the stockade.

1096
01:50:31,958 --> 01:50:35,223
他们需要所有能用的人手
They need every guy they can get.

1097
01:50:35,428 --> 01:50:40,092
但你的伤口会裂开 他们会知道是你杀了那个士官
But your side will open up. They'll find out you killed that soldier.

1098
01:50:40,400 --> 01:50:45,099
只要我向部队报到 他们就会照顾我的
Once I report in to the company, they'll take care of me.

1099
01:50:45,305 --> 01:50:48,672
你绝对到不了的 到处都有人在巡逻
You'll never make it! There's patrols all over!

1100
01:50:48,875 --> 01:50:51,935
我到得了！我知道捷径
I'll make it. I know a shortcut.

1101
01:50:54,314 --> 01:50:59,115
留到天亮再说吧！ 或许你会改变心意
Stay till morning. Maybe you'll change your mind.

1102
01:51:06,726 --> 01:51:10,662
普威特，不要走 我会照你的话去做
Oh, Prew, don't go! I'll do anything you want!

1103
01:51:11,564 --> 01:51:16,160
我们可以一起回美国 甚至我们可以结婚
We can go back to the States together. We can even get married.

1104
01:51:18,972 --> 01:51:23,932
 若你走了，我再也见不到你  对不起
  Lf you go, I'll never see you again.   I'm sorry.

1105
01:51:29,382 --> 01:51:31,680
你为什么想回去？
Why do you want to go back?

1106
01:51:31,885 --> 01:51:34,376
陆军根本视你如粪土…
The Army treated you like dirt...

1107
01:51:34,587 --> 01:51:38,353
经常殴打你，还害你朋友丧命
...gave you an awful going over, got your friend killed!

1108
01:51:38,558 --> 01:51:40,549
你为什么想回去？
Why do you want to go back?

1109
01:51:40,760 --> 01:51:43,593
我为什么想回去？ 因为我是军人
Why do I want to go back? I'm a soldier.

1110
01:51:44,064 --> 01:51:49,400
军人！一个常备兵！一个陆军！ 一个准备当兵三十年的人！
A soldier! A regular. From the regular Army! A 30 year man!

1111
01:51:51,304 --> 01:51:55,536
外面正在实施灯火管制 所以我得把灯关掉
I gotta turn off the lights because of the blackout outside.

1112
01:52:09,189 --> 01:52:13,182
 山上有伞兵降落  我并不担心他们
  Parachutists landed in the hills.   They don't worry me.

1113
01:52:13,393 --> 01:52:18,592
 我担心的是破坏份子  我打赌他们一定遍布全岛
  Saboteurs is what worries me.   I bet they're all over the islands.

1114
01:53:31,771 --> 01:53:33,068
不要动！
Halt!

1115
01:53:35,708 --> 01:53:36,936
不要动！
Halt!

1116
01:53:48,588 --> 01:53:49,612
不要动！
Halt!

1117
01:54:26,159 --> 01:54:30,425
 你认识这个人吗？上士  是的，长官
  Do you know this man, sergeant?   Yes, sir.

1118
01:54:30,630 --> 01:54:35,226
他没有任何身分证明 他们找到有他名字的卡片
He didn't have any regular I.D. They found a card with his name.

1119
01:54:35,435 --> 01:54:39,531
好像是俱乐部的会员证 新国会俱乐部
Seems to be a membership in a club. The New Congress Club.

1120
01:54:39,939 --> 01:54:42,237
你最好处理一下
You'd better take care of this.

1121
01:54:46,012 --> 01:54:47,411
他是你的朋友吗？
Was he your friend?

1122
01:54:47,614 --> 01:54:51,607
他一定是想回到海滩上的部队
He must've been trying to reach our company up the beach.

1123
01:54:51,818 --> 01:54:53,479
那么为什么他不停止？
Then why didn't he halt?

1124
01:54:53,686 --> 01:54:56,655
他是死脑筋但却是个好军人
He was a hard head, but he was a good soldier.

1125
01:54:56,856 --> 01:55:00,019
他是我认识的所有人中 最爱陆军的
He loved the Army more than anyone else I knew.

1126
01:55:00,226 --> 01:55:03,218
我明白了，很遗憾，上士
I see. I'm sorry, sergeant.

1127
01:55:18,745 --> 01:55:21,213
你就是不能从善如流
You just couldn't play it smart.

1128
01:55:22,048 --> 01:55:26,246
不过是要你打拳罢了 可是你这个死脑筋就是不肯
All you had to do is box, but no, not you, you hard head.

1129
01:55:26,452 --> 01:55:30,980
好笑的是，今年没有拳击冠军
Funny thing is, there won't be a boxing championship this year.

1130
01:55:37,897 --> 01:55:43,529
没有看过死人吗？ 把尸体抬出去
Ain't you ever seen a dead man? Let's get this body out of here!

1131
01:56:05,391 --> 01:56:07,518
真美，是吧？
It's very beautiful, isn't it?

1132
01:56:12,098 --> 01:56:16,626
我想这是我此生见过 最美的一个地方
I think it's the most beautiful place I ever saw in my life.

1133
01:56:17,170 --> 01:56:20,162
我几乎能看见我工作的地方
I can almost see where I worked from here.

1134
01:56:24,210 --> 01:56:26,144
听说有个传说
There's a legend.

1135
01:56:27,080 --> 01:56:30,777
如果花环漂向海岸 表示你还会再回来
If they float in toward shore, you'll come back.

1136
01:56:31,184 --> 01:56:33,448
如果是向外漂，你就不会回来
If they float out, you won't.

1137
01:56:39,092 --> 01:56:41,117
我不会再回来了
I won't come back.

1138
01:56:42,795 --> 01:56:46,390
我的未婚夫在十二月七日被杀
You see, my fiancé was killed on December 7 th.

1139
01:56:47,200 --> 01:56:51,330
 真是遗憾  他原是个轰炸机飞行员
  Oh, I'm sorry.   He was a bomber pilot.

1140
01:56:51,537 --> 01:56:54,529
当他把飞机滑到停机坪边缘…
He taxied his plane to the edge of the apron...

1141
01:56:54,741 --> 01:56:57,232
日军直接击中他
...and the Japs made a direct hit on it.

1142
01:56:58,011 --> 01:57:00,639
或许你曾在报上看过消息
Maybe you read about it in the papers.

1143
01:57:01,047 --> 01:57:03,607
他获授银星勋章
He was awarded the Silver Star.

1144
01:57:04,384 --> 01:57:08,946
军方将勋章送给他母亲 她写信给我，要我保留它
They sent it to his mother. She wrote me she wanted me to have it.

1145
01:57:09,422 --> 01:57:11,652
她真好
That's very fine of her.

1146
01:57:12,458 --> 01:57:15,586
南方人都很好
They're very fine people. Southern people.

1147
01:57:16,396 --> 01:57:18,830
他以某位将军的名字为名
He was named after a general.

1148
01:57:19,599 --> 01:57:21,464
罗勃
Robert E. Lee...

1149
01:57:22,468 --> 01:57:24,129
普威特
...Prewitt.

1150
01:57:25,204 --> 01:57:26,193
谁？
Who?

1151
01:57:27,774 --> 01:57:30,937
罗勃普威特
Robert E. Lee Prewitt.

1152
01:57:34,280 --> 01:57:36,612
真是个愚蠢的老名字吧？
Isn't that a silly old name?


